                        <interp inst="t18410823-name-1733" type="given" value="JOHN HENRY"></interp>JOHN HENRY ALDRIDGE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, in Hoi ling-street. I produce seven handkerchiefs pawned with me for 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., on the 24th of July, think by the prisoner—I am not certain—I gate this duplicate for them.</p>
